1 for teachers; but in emergencies, which must be declared, the state board may
2 authorize the issuance of provisional certificates based on not less than
3 two (2) years of college training.
4 SECTION 4. An emergency existing therefor, which emergency is hereby
5 declared to exist, this act shall be in full force and effect on and after
6 July 1, 2025.

